Mariko<i>-sama!</i>

40
00:03:06,082 --> 00:03:07,665
Bapa Surgawi,

41
00:03:07,749 --> 00:03:13,165
kami serahkan kepada-Mu,
pelayan setia-Mu, Mariko<i>-sama.</i>

42
